This is the speaker embedding repository.
This repo is to collect various speaker embedders.

Author: Lim Zhi Hao		Date: 2022-03-22

These embedding networks can be used in:
	1) Speaker Verification and Identification
	2) Speaker Diarization
	3) Speaker Extraction
	4) Antispoofing for Speaker Verification
	5) Text-to-Speech
	6) Voice Conversion

--------------------------------------------------------------------

For a start, check conda version:

	conda -V

As of 2022-03-22, the scripts are tested in conda 4.12.0. 

********************************************************************


--------------------------------------------------------------------

Then initate the conda environment using the "speaker_embeddings.yml"

	conda env create --file speaker_embeddings.yml
	conda activate speaker_embeddings


********************************************************************


--------------------------------------------------------------------

Finally, please run the following:

	bash run.sh

This will run the pipeline on "test_audio/librispeech_test-other"

To learn more about the pipeline, please see scripts/run_batch.py

********************************************************************
